<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>

  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">


  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.4.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.7.2/css/all.css"
        integrity="sha384-fnmOCqbTlWIlj8LyTjo7mOUStjsKC4pOpQbqyi7RrhN7udi9RwhKkMHpvLbHG9Sr" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <% stylesheet_link_tag "bootstrap" %>
  <% stylesheet_link_tag "music" %>
  <title>Muzify - music station</title>

</head>

<body>


<nav class="navbar-default">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="navbar-brand">

      <%= link_to developers_new_path do %><%= image_tag(("뮤지파이4.png"), :class => 'logo', :alt => 'Lattes theme logo') %>
        <!--        <img class="logo" width=250px; height=200px;-->
        <!--                                  src="img/뮤지파이4.png"-->
        <!--                                  alt="Lattes theme logo">-->
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <div>
      <ul class="nav">


        <li>
          <%= link_to "Contemporary", index_index_path, class: 'page-scroll' %>

          <!--          <a class="page-scroll" href="index.html#contemporary">Contemporary</a>-->
        </li>

        <li>
          <%= link_to "Contact", developers_new_path(:anchor => 'contact'), class: 'page-selected' %>

        </li>
        <li>
          <%= link_to "Memory", new_message_path, class: 'page-scroll' %>
        </li>

        <li>
          <%= link_to "About", developers_new_path, class: 'page-selected' %>
        </li>


      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>

</nav>

<header>
  <div class="container">

    <div class="title">
      <div class="comment">당신을 위한 음악을 들려줄게요.</div>
      <div class="heading">Muzify Music Station</div>
      <a href="#developer" class="page-scroll btn btn-xl">건의하기</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</header>
<div class="content">

  <section id="logo">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <div class="section-title">
            <h2>뮤지파이 로고</h2>
            <p>뮤지파이는 현재 제가 활동하고 있는 서울대 보컬크루의 이름과 같답니다. 디자인한 로고들을 살펴볼까요?</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <%= image_tag(("뮤지파이.png"), :class => 'img-responsive') %>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <%= image_tag(("뮤지파이6.jpeg"), :class => 'img-responsive') %>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-4">
            <%= image_tag(("뮤지파이3.png"), :class => 'img-responsive') %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <%= image_tag(("뮤지파이5.png"), :class => 'img-responsive') %>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <%= image_tag(("뮤지파이2.png"), :class => 'img-responsive') %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>


  <section id="developer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-5">
          <div class="section-title">
            <h2>개발자</h2>
            <p>개발자를 위한 한 마디가 큰 응원이 됩니다.</p>

            <figure>
              <%= image_tag(("ellie.jpg"), :class => 'develop_image', :alt => 'Image') %>
              <figcaption>
                <h3 class="figure-title">강수진</h3>

                <p class="figure-description">서울대 전기정보공학부 16학번</p>
                <p>AI, 데이터, 백엔드에 관심있고 요즘은 앱개발과 인공지능 관련 미디어아트를 공부하고 있어요</p>


                <p><a class="btn btn-social-icon btn-git" href="https://github.com/Ella77"><i
                  class="fab fa-git"></i> </a>
                  <a class="btn btn-social-icon btn-git"
                     href="https://www.facebook.com/ellie.kang.33"><i
                    class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a></p>
              </figcaption>
            </figure>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">


          <div class="section-title">
            <h2>그 날의 나를 기록하기</h2>
            <p>오늘의 감성에 맞는 음악을 추천받은 당신, 메시지를 남겨주세요.<br>서비스 건의사항도 받아요.</p>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <h3>Contact</h3>
          <p>Ibk communication center 302, Seoul National University</p>
          <p><i class="fa fa-phone"></i> +10 2651 3241</p>
          <p><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>ksjbang@gmail.com</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <h3>Update</h3>

          <p><i class="fa fa-check"></i> <span class="day">실시간</span></p>
          <p><i class="fa fa-check"></i> <span class="day">엠넷 차트 기준</span></p>

        </div>


        <div class="col-md-6">


          <%= form_for @developer, :form_class => 'form-control', :class => 'button' do |f| %>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="form-group">
                  <%= f.text_field :name, :id => "name", :placeholder => "이름 *" %>
                  <p class="help-block text-danger"></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="form-group">
                  <%= f.text_field :email, :id => "email", :placeholder => "답장받을 이메일 *" %>
                  <p class="help-block text-danger"></p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="form-group">

                  <%= f.text_field :message, :id => "message", :placeholder => "메시지 *" %>
                  <p class="help-block text-danger"></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="clearfix"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                <div id="success"></div>
                <%= f.submit "등록", :class => "button", onclick: 'alert("메시지를 보냈습니다");' %>
          <% end %>

          </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


  </section>


  <footer class="footer">

    <p><strong>Made by Ellie Kang</strong></p>

  </footer>

</div>

</body>
</html>
